The government is determined to invest more on youth skills by building Vocational Training Colleges in each district in the country. Responding Mbulu MP Flatei Massasy’s question who sought to know about government’s plan to boost development vocational training programme in his constituency, Minister of Education, Science, Technology and Vocational Training, Prof Joyce Ndalichako said the government is in the process of building the institutions not only in Mbulu but across the country However, Prof Ndalichako advised Mbulu residents to get such services at available institutions including Community Development Colleges as well as VETA located at different parts of the country